abstract: ROCHESTER, Dec. 14 -- James C. Stuart, representing the Skating Club of New York, won the senior men's compulsory figures competition over Gary F. Jones, of the Syracuse Figure Skating Club today in the North Atlantic figure skating championships at the new Skating Club today in the North Atlantic figure skatign championships at the new Frank Ritter Memorial Ice Rink on the Rochester Institute of Technology campus.
